Name: Yo My Yo!
About the game: Yo My Yo! is a simplistic 2D racing game, in which the player must avoid collisions on the road during a given time. While it sounds easy, you will find yourself in very peculiar situations. Key features of the game: Partially random enemy spawn; Unpredictable movement of some enemies; Colorful 2D sprites based on the shapes of real cars; Steam achievements; Changing day and night cycle; Finest rage-inducing experience.
